Package: nlaR
Title: Interface to the National Lakes Assessment
Version: 0.3
Authors@R: person("Joseph", "Stachelek", email = "stachel2@msu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Client for programmatic access and to the 2007 and 2012 National 
  Lakes Assessment database <https://www.epa.gov/national-aquatic-resource-surveys/nla> 
  for representative lakes in the lower 48 states of the contiguous US.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
